  "body": "<p>Happy Thanksgiving! I'm thankful for a lot of things, but wanted to mention how thankful I am that YOU are coming to read my blog. I truly appreciate it! Every month I feel like I don't have quite enough time to use my SC kits, but this time, I carved out a few days and was able to get caught up on several occasions I wanted to document. Love the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/park-ave?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico Park Ave kits</a> and the mix of colors and patterns. I incorporated various techniques like stamping, sewing and painting with watercolors. If you're looking to get only 1 or 2 add-ons, I would highly recommend <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/dec-sb-add-on-2?aff=6cc2c70f\">Helmsley</a> and <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/dec-sb-add-on-1?aff=6cc2c70f\">Ritz</a>. Here's how my projects came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598325983516-0K8FJ47IBD5I5WNL9EH9/18a-IMG_2043.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"18b-IMG_2051.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326018273-P1SXRVUUBS77897ZH3JX/18b-IMG_2051.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"18c-IMG_2017.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326017259-LLYRV651AI3PKQJILADC/18c-IMG_2017.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18d-.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326019046-1DGISAPBSQQKL0DYYA34/18d-.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18e-IMG_2011.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326019767-ID0ZX9KKFWSP6Z4QK6ZK/18e-IMG_2011.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18g-IMG_2019.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326022159-6OBM50VHTG6KNYGDIYD3/18g-IMG_2019.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18j-IMG_2053.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326112407-E3NYWMB7SMS5ZX55LT6R/18j-IMG_2053.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18k-IMG_2037.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326112223-53AXO839GKR01NTPPZ38/18k-IMG_2037.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18f-IMG_2036.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326151856-56H9CC3G6BPPZXLIC26U/18f-IMG_2036.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18i-IMG_2048.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326152151-3EI9MQL32UD7CSC9SAP0/18i-IMG_2048.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>For Project Life spreads, I really wanted to utilize the pocket pages for the opening party for Hello Kitty Con. I ended up taking quite a few photos that will likely just go into a mini, but I did want to tell this story in my regular album as well. I used the good vibes only card (even though I really wanted to hoard it) from <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/dec-pl-add-on-1?aff=6cc2c70f\">Grand Central</a>. The stamps from <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/dec-pl-add-on-2?aff=6cc2c70f\">Lenox Hill</a> look very Hello Kitty-ish. And of course I love the look of the Kal script wood alpha too.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326212462-97085JF6LR2G1K0BZLWY/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Using the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/park-ave-project-life-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Project Life main kit only</a> I created a spread covering 3 full days of fun.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598326232109-H03SLZJ28WIRYRM78PE5/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>You can shop for all <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/park-ave?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico Park Ave kits here</a> and see <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/project-folders/6035-park-avenue?aff=6cc2c70f\">all my projects here</a>.</p><p><em>Keep in mind that </em><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\"><em>subscribers</em></a><em> can shop the pre-sale each month at noon EST on the 27th. Others need to wait until the clock strikes midnight tonight. </em><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\"><em>Become a subscriber</em></a><em> and get in on all the benefits and rewards that </em><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\"><em>Studio Calico</em></a><em> has to offer!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
